Word Accentuation Test - Chicago

Source: R/data.R
WATC.Rd

Word Accentuation Test - Chicago data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(WATC)

Format

A data frame with 833 observations and 59 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4, ADNI1, ADNIGO

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 21, ..., 10819

  • VISCODE character Visit code , with options: 4_init, 4_bl, 4_m12

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • EXAMDATE Examination Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • DONE character Was assessment/procedure done? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • NDREASON character If No, reason not done 1=Participant Unable for Cognitive Reasons ; 10=Not called for by protocol ; 11=Not a Spanish-speaking participant ; 2=Participant Unable for Other Reasons (Physical, auditory, etc.) ; 3=Participant/Study Partner Refused ; 7=Site Error ; 8=Other Reason ; 9=Unknown Decoded Value: Yes

  • SOURCE character Information Source 1=Participant Visit ; 2=Telephone Call/Video Call Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC1 character 1. polígamo 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC2 character 2. búlgaro 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC3 character 3. cúpula 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC4 character 4. sándalo 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC5 character 5. célibe 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC6 character 6. metrópoli 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC7 character 7. albedrío 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC8 character 8. parónimo 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC9 character 9. procónsul 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC10 character 10. abogacía 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC11 character 11. acólito 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC12 character 12. rabí 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC13 character 13. volátil 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC14 character 14. diámetro 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC15 character 15. cánon 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC16 character 16. inverosímil 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC17 character 17. ámbar 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC18 character 18. alegoría 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC19 character 19. isótopo 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC20 character 20. pífano 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC21 character 21. sístole 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC22 character 22. ínfulas 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC23 character 23. gélido 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC24 character 24. hipérbole 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC25 character 25. peroné 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC26 character 26. retruécano 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC27 character 27. tórrido 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC28 character 28. táctil 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC29 character 29. anómalo 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC30 character 30. díscolo 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC31 character 31. pécora 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC32 character 32. púgil 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC33 character 33. cóncavo 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC36 character 36. sílice 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC37 character 37. apátrida 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC38 character 38. láudano 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC39 character 39. acullá 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • WATC40 character 40. supérstite 0=Incorrect ; 1=Correct Decoded Value: Yes

  • RAWSCORE numeric Raw Score: Sum of scores Range value: 18, ..., 40

  • ID numeric Record ID Range value: 16546, ..., 106657

  • SITEID numeric Site ID Range value: 2, ..., 941

  • USERDATE User Create Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • USERDATE2 User Last Modify Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • DD_CRF_VERSION_LABEL character CRF Version Label , with options: v1

  • LANGUAGE_CODE character Language Code e=English Decoded Value: Yes

  • HAS_QC_ERROR character Has Quality Check Error 0=Does not have QC error or QC error has been approved ; 1=Has QC error Decoded Value: Yes

  • update_stamp POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
